'''Tamaru-hime''' (多満留姫) is a {{ill|Kunitsukami|ja|国津神|1=Kunitsukami|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kunitsukami|13=User:Immanuelle/Kunitsukami|qq=}} (earthly deity) and a goddess in the {{ill|Suwa Faith|ja|諏訪信仰|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Suwa Faith|qq=}}, a belief system native to the {{ill|Suwa region|ja|諏訪地方|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Suwa region|qq=}} of {{ill|Nagano Prefecture|ja|長野県|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Nagano Prefecture|qq=}}.

[[File:Tamaru-hime_Shrine_1.jpg|thumb|200px|Taru-hime Shrine]]

== Overview ==
Tamaru-hime is said to be the daughter of {{ill|Moreya no Kami|ja|洩矢神|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Moreya no Kami|qq=}} and married {{ill|Izuhayao no Mikoto|ja|出早雄命|1=Izuhayao-no-Mikoto|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Izuhayao no Mikoto|13=User:Immanuelle/Izuhayao-no-Mikoto|qq=}}
, who is the son of {{ill|Takeminakata|ja|建御名方神|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Takeminakata|qq=}} and {{ill|Yasakatome|ja|八坂刀売神|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yasakatome|qq=}}.<ref>"Shincho Shrine Introduction: {{ill|Moreya Shrine|ja|洩矢神社|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Moreya Shrine|qq=}}," {{ill|Nagano Shrine Agency|ja|長野県神社庁|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Nagano Shrine Agency|qq=}} official website.</ref><ref>"Genealogy of the Moriya clan," {{ill|Suwa Historical Association|ja|諏訪教育会|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Suwa Historical Association|qq=}}, 1936, pp. 31–34.</ref>

In the {{ill|Genealogy of the Moriya clan|ja|神長守矢氏系譜|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Genealogy of the Moriya clan|qq=}}, Tamaru-hime is described as the consort of Izuhaya no Mikoto. Another source alternatively claims that she was married to {{ill|Takeminakata|ja|建御名方神|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Takeminakata|qq=}} and gave birth to Izuhaya no Mikoto.<ref>Yonekawa Kazuhiko, "Revised Suwa Genealogy," ''Suwa Genealogy, Vol. 2,'' Iida Kotaro, 1921, p. 19.</ref>

The goddess is sometimes referred to as '''Tamaru-hime no Mikoto''' (多留姫命). However, in most contexts, she is distinguished from {{ill|Taru-hime no Mikoto|ja|多留比売神|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Taru-hime no Mikoto|qq=}}, who is commonly regarded as a child of Takeminakata.<ref>Morii Mikio, "Genealogy of Takeminakata," ''Suwa Shrine Historical Records,'' Nakamura Jinnosuke, 1910, p. 10.</ref>

== Lineage ==
[[File:Moriya Family Tree - 守矢氏系図.png|170px|thumbnail|center|The first five generations of the {{ill|Moriya clan|ja|守矢氏|1=Moriya clan|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Moriya clan|13=User:Immanuelle/Moriya clan|qq=}} lineage (from {{ill|Moreya no Kami|ja|洩矢神|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Moreya no Kami|qq=}} to {{ill|Yasugami|ja|八櫛神|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yasugami|qq=}}).]]

Tamaru-hime is the daughter of {{ill|Moreya no Kami|ja|洩矢神|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Moreya no Kami|qq=}} and the sister of {{ill|Moritaku-no-Kami|ja|洩宅神|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Moritaku-no-Kami|qq=}}.<ref>"Genealogy of the Moriya clan," {{ill|Suwa Historical Association|ja|諏訪教育会|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Suwa Historical Association|qq=}}, 1936, pp. 33–34.</ref>

She married {{ill|Izuhayao no Mikoto|ja|出早雄命|1=Izuhayao-no-Mikoto|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Izuhayao no Mikoto|13=User:Immanuelle/Izuhayao-no-Mikoto|qq=}}
, the son of {{ill|Takeminakata|ja|建御名方神|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Takeminakata|qq=}} and {{ill|Yasakatome|ja|八坂刀売神|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yasakatome|qq=}}. Together, they had the following children:
* {{ill|Kameba no Kami|ja|可毛羽神|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kameba no Kami|qq=}}
* {{ill|Wakagi-hime|ja|若木比売神|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Wakagi-hime|qq=}}
* {{ill|Kusanoi-hime|ja|草奈井比売神|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kusanoi-hime|qq=}}
* {{ill|Itsuhayahime-no-Mikoto|lt=Itsuhayahime-no-Mikoto|lt=Itsuhaya-hime|ja|出早比売命|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Itsuhaya-hime|qq=}}
* {{ill|Yatsugata no Sukune no Kami|ja|八縣宿禰神|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yatsugata no Sukune no Kami|qq=}}

